{"tid":2516882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署：因有人呼籲到喪禮現場聲援胡志偉 故駁回申請 稱可安排視像方式參與","createTime":"2021-05-05T03:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T03:19:55.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2c008702d98662ff5145397a63fe4c80bc50fe5","tid":2516882,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"懲教署不批准胡志偉外出奔喪 稱可安排視像方式參與<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》引述民主黨成員表示，民主派初選案被還柙的該黨前主席胡志偉，其父親上月中去世，胡志偉早前向懲教署申請外出奔喪，署方初步否決申請，只容許他以視像方式觀看喪禮。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回應說，會一視同仁按現行保安機制處理所有在囚人士提出相關申請。根據條例，署方會考慮在囚人士的所犯罪行、保安風險、押解路線、地點安全等各項保安因素。<br />\n<br />\n署方近日留意到喪禮的日期、時間及地點較早時被社交媒體廣泛報道，網上亦有人士號召喪禮當日到場支持，經保安評估後，為保障懲教人員、在囚人士及公眾人士的安全，署方決定不批准有關申請。<br />\n<br />\n署方表示，對在囚人士家人離世深表同情，希望提供其他可行途徑協助，近年署方致力發展智慧監獄，傳輸視像訊息是主要發展範疇，因此決定應用有關科技，首次安排以視像方式參與喪禮讓在囚人士考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589294-20210505.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589294-20210505.htm&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=033a833a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589294-20210505.htm&h=0b50f2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589294-20210505.htm</a>"},{"pid":"98bd732c8d9799ec63bd17cdf0654d946be30a31","tid":2516882,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事但搵條友講2句就話有風險真係幾好做"},{"pid":"5b8e040698fda4ccac4b0ac9615684b9b9689792","tid":2516882,"uid":4709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"視像坐監有冇得諗"},{"pid":"b64c5d5cdd3cf17cb3d8d579dbaf9b7fd4b765ce","tid":2516882,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b8e040698fda4ccac4b0ac9615684b9b9689792","tid":2516882,"uid":4709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"視像坐監有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:16:02.000Z","msg":"Zoom報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8d4f36ec79f92be922514f443cff2f1b10acff","tid":2516882,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b8e040698fda4ccac4b0ac9615684b9b9689792","tid":2516882,"uid":4709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"視像坐監有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"中國幾十年前已經做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbe2d70a61c523e58c4d4e62a363d5396600c82","tid":2516882,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"想搞分化？"},{"pid":"3217a6f7ae5da7ec16f40bdd7b18c1209d11ed7d","tid":2516882,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"國家安全洗80億<br />\n警隊年年洗200幾億<br />\n但都冇能力保證一個葬禮安全<br />\n要禁止一個 未被定罪 嘅人<br />\n出席至親嘅葬禮"}]}